The cryosphere component is directly related to ocean sea-level, therefore is indirectly related to changes in the atmosphere and biosphere.</skos:definition>    <skos:broader rdf:resource="e1f20631-b5b9-438c-b5c2-b1fa0fce100a"/> </skos:Concept> </rdf:RDF>
